{"tid":1618760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港市民鼻敏感同皮膚敏感","createTime":"2019-10-04T06:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T00:18:54.000Z","uid":267572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cef86f75a257f128e8cf77e2a25501caa4a21ee0","tid":1618760,"uid":267572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:28:22.000Z","msg":"快d 约黄色醫生。<br />\n<br />\n耳鼻喉科：因鼻敏感而要帶口罩。<br />\n<br />\n皮膚科：因對太陽UV 敏感，要用全面罩。<br />\n<br />\n以後，任何時候都带住兩張醫生纸，保平安。<br />\n<br />\n我耳鼻喉醫生要9 Oct 先有位睇症。"},{"pid":"c58b6f4c5db4d5711eac1e40aa71b11c91baffe2","tid":1618760,"uid":113022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"普通科咪得.."},{"pid":"fe1c2d57eb32451ff1c718360352eda3a585ebd0","tid":1618760,"uid":269083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:44:37.000Z","msg":"為他人着想，當我們出現呼吸道感染病徵時 (咳嗽或打噴嚏...) 就記得要帶口罩。<br />\n<br />\n衛生處佩戴口罩指引：<br />\n<br />\n何時要佩戴口罩？<br />\n1. 保護自己：當我們需<br />\n要照顧呼吸道受感染<br />\n的患者時；或在流<br />\n感大流行／高峰期期<br />\n間進入醫院或診所。<br />\n<br />\n2. 保護他人避免受感染：<br />\n當我們出現呼吸道感染病徵時，如發燒、流<br />\n鼻水、咳嗽或打噴嚏等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/her/use_mask_properly_pamphlet.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fher%2Fuse_mask_properly_pamphlet.pdf&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3iaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=62fa1a0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/her/use_mask_properly_pamphlet.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"f4d54900f7c4807744ec7f24eb07178a92a9c81c","tid":1618760,"uid":267572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c58b6f4c5db4d5711eac1e40aa71b11c91baffe2","tid":1618760,"uid":113022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"普通科咪得.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:49:30.000Z","msg":"可以，但專科有牙力多些。特别是缐"},{"pid":"1d530a5c9ac0f10d1cd0336dfca6efdcc5c120c3","tid":1618760,"uid":267572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe1c2d57eb32451ff1c718360352eda3a58